   Meanwhile, at level 3, you will find Portuguese paintings and
   sculptures.
     * Padrão dos Descobrimentos / A Tribute to the Age of Discovery

   The monolith structure was built in 1960 for paying tribute to the
   500th anniversary of Henry the Navigator’s death. The design is
   intentionally made to appreciate those who were involved in the Golden
   Age of Discovery, such as Vasco da Gama, Fernão de Magalhães, and Pedro
   Álves Cabral. This extraordinary monument would be excellent for your
   historical trip.


   How much things cost in Lisbon?

   Items

   Cost (in PHP)

   Accommodation

   A 4-person dorm room starts from PHP971 (but sell out quickly), while a
   private room costs PHP2590. Hotel rooms range from PHP3,885 to PHP7,123
   for a good clean room with private bathroom.

   Transportation

   Taxi charges from PHP777 to PHP970 while a single metro ticket costs
   PHP93 and 24 hours ticket public transport costs PHP421.

   Food & drink

   An evening meal in a tourist restaurant with a glass of wine costs
   PHP1,600 - PHP1,900. A light meal in a café PHP259 to PHP323. An
   espresso PHP39 and a cake PHP58 for breakfast.

   Medical consultation

   Consultations usually cost PHP485, emergency treatment start from
   PHP971 to PHP1295, and overnight stays cost PHP1618 per night.


